/* ==========================================================================
  FAMILY SHARING SERVICE (.todo) — v4 shim-aware scaffold
  Purpose: Private, role-aware sharing across a single family/family-fund:
           plans, sessions, storehouse updates, calendars, etc.

  Principles:
    1) Clear IA (organized nav + routes)
    2) Intuitive flow (compose → preview → post)
    3) Consistent design (btn/card/alert/states)
    4) Event-driven glue (recipes/inventory/calendar/... updates)
    5) Respect sabbath/quiet-hours; support undo, NBAs, empty states
    6) Background-safe: posting is handled by a shim that survives navigation
========================================================================== */

